{"tw": {"3782910": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Goblin Nest", "steam_appid": 3782910, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Goblin Nest is a simple resource management game. Build your nest and increase your population by raiding villages and bringing defeated enemies back to your base.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help Lilith rebuild Evil and bring balance back to the world. <br><br><strong>Story</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Goblins went extinct! That is until... Lilith, Daughter of Hell, brought your kind back from the dead. Build your nest, capture powerful enemies, regrow your population, and take over the land.   <br>  <br><strong>Build</strong>  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3782910/extras/5025a6b84b3fd4a49d70155600edde59.poster.avif?t=1776129411\" width=1170 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3782910/extras/5025a6b84b3fd4a49d70155600edde59.webm?t=1776129411\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3782910/extras/5025a6b84b3fd4a49d70155600edde59.mp4?t=1776129411\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong>Manage population's mood, gold and rations. Figure out ways to optimize cell placements for efficiency. Grow and decorate your nest into a multi layer, self sustaining factory.   <br> <br><strong>Customize</strong>  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3782910/extras/94658c8b7c69685bbab9d453bd822b02.poster.avif?t=1776129411\" width=1170 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3782910/extras/94658c8b7